Notes for Users of this document: Coding is more Phonetic in Baraha. Special care – Baraha coding uses ‘e’ and ‘o’ (in Sanskrit) 
for sound E and O. we have used capital letters as it matches with Unicode/general conventions in this document. ~g is nasal of ka varga (gna) ~j is nasal of cha varga (jya) H is visargam Vedic/Swara symbols – q anudAttam, # swaritam, 
$ dheerga swaritam, & avagraha,  ~M nasal symbol ushmAn codes s, S, Sha (saraswati, Sankar, puShpam) Confirm corrections given in TS 3 kANDam are incorporated as per Version 1.1 dated November 30, 2020. Kindly notify any major errors or inadvertent deletions to mail id- vedavms@gmail.com OM namaH paramAtmanE, SrI mahAgaNapatayE namaH, SrI guruByO namaH haqriqH OM 3	kRuShNa yajurvEdIya taittirIya saMhitAyaM tRutIyaM kANDaM 3.1	tRutIyakANDE prathamaH praSnaH - nyUnakarmABidhAnaM TS 3.1.1.1 praqjApa#tirakAmayata praqjAH sRu#jEqyEtiq sa tapO#&tapyataq sa saqrpAna#sRujataq sO#&kAmayata praqjAH sRu#jEqyEtiq sadviqtIya#matapyataq sa vayA(gg)#sya sRujataq sO#&kAmayata praqjAH sRu#jEqyEtiq sa tRuqtIya#matapyataq sa EqtaM dI$kShitavAqda-ma#paSyaqt tama#vadaqt tatOq vai sa praqjA a#sRujataq yat tapa#staqptvA dI$kShitavAqdaM ~Mvada#ti praqjA Eqva tadyaja#mAnaH - [  ]    1 TS 3.1.1.2 sRujatEq yadvai dI$kShiqtO#&mEqddhyaM paSyaqtyapA$smAddIqkShAkrA#matiq nIla#masyaq harOq vyE$tyaba#ddhaqM manO# daqridraqM cakShuqH sUryOq jyOti#ShAq(gg)qSrEShThOq dIkShEq mA mA#hAsIqrityA#haq nAsmA$ddIqkShA&pa#krAmatiq nAsyaq nIlaqM na harOq vyE#tiq yadvai dI$kShiqtama#Biqvar.Sha#tidiqvyA ApO&SA$ntAq OjOq bala#M dIqkShAM - [  ]    2 TS 3.1.1.3 tapO$&syaqnirGna#ntyundaqtIr bala#M dhaqttaujO# dhattaq bala#M dhattaq mA mE# dIqkShAM mA tapOqnirva#dhiqShTEtyA#haiq tadEqva sarva#mAqtman dha#ttEq nAsyaujOq balaqM na dIqkShAM na tapOqnirGna#ntyaqgnirvai dI$kShiqtasya# dEqvatAq sO$&smAdEqtar.hi#tiqra i#vaq yar.hiq yAtiq tamI$Svaqra(gm) rakShA(gm)#siq hantO$ -  [  ]     3 TS 3.1.1.4
